The focus on software verification also suggests that the paper could belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of formal methods for verification, which could place it in the Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of tree decomposition techniques, which could place it in the Scientific Computing (cs.SC) sub-category.
